content:
This page has an interactive map associated with it. Click here to view a map of free-to-play music track unlock locations in more detail.
This article is about the free-to-play music track list. For the full list, see Music.

Most Free-to-play music tracks can be unlocked by all players, although there are a small number of tracks that are unlocked exclusively during certain quests (such as Dragon Slayer I's music tracks), in the fight with Bryophyta, or during holiday events.

Trivia[edit | edit source]

  • There were a few tracks previously available in free-to-play before becoming members-only:
    • Parade was accessible near Lumber Yard and Jolly Boar Inn until the release of Grand Exchange on 26 February 2015.
    • Legion and Gaol could be unlocked at Bandit Camp and north of it, respectively, before an update on 28 April 2021.
    • Getting Down to Business and Illusive could be unlocked during 2021 Halloween event.
  • Egypt is currently the only free-to-play track unlockable exclusively by using Classic music area mode.
